{"tid":1324253,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"見住你地屌林卓廷同個社工有咩用? 唔好on9啦","createTime":"2019-07-16T13:35:13.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-16T13:36:08.000Z","uid":160991,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"4a2460313addba83d0830173d88ccb130e42e67c","tid":1324253,"uid":160991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T13:35:13.000Z","msg":"明白你地嬲<br />\n但唔該唔好發洩喺佢地身上<br />\n搵同路人做磨心好咩?<br />\n<br />\n你咁樣圍，班高層都係唔會出黎<br />\n喺度難為細既職員<br />\n佢地喺度<br />\n你地都係得個屌字<br />\n佢地唔喺度<br />\n最後咪又係散<br />\n<br />\n可以日日圍新城市/總部<br />\n林卓廷同個社工都係話比大家知<br />\n你咁樣圍埋屌都係冇用<br />\n<br />\n而家見到有幾個屌佢地個post<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">記住不分化不割蓆</span></strong><br />\n呢度有好多一毛見到機會就會分化"},{"pid":"8a365b97a50114ac5b3913d3840c4c97d042f3ca","tid":1324253,"uid":160991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T13:35:50.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">不分化</span></strong>"},{"pid":"ed0248bbe604b50d8f770cdb7c9e38422969e3e7","tid":1324253,"uid":160991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T13:36:08.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">不割蓆</span></strong>"}]}